{"tid":2093713,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[創科局/科學園/HKNOIT] 台北信義區無人駕駛巴士半夜測試","createTime":"2020-07-04T04:55:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-04T04:57:06.000Z","uid":11598,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4718344355cf2d472fb2537b5288310c084d41ab","tid":2093713,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T04:55:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ti3TRRO368Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DTi3TRRO368Q&d=C%2Fe7%2FQel5OtnIpuNpUi2IEUPjIZJXyGGplxIPwZjN5A%3D&h=3ec6374f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ti3TRRO368Q</a><br />\n<br />\n台北市嘅無人駕駛巴士已經開始測試緊<br />\n應該9月就會開始真係載客<br />\n可能有啲人會屌話會唔會影響巴士司機生計<br />\n佢哋而家嘅定位係夜間巴士<br />\n台北一到凌晨就無巴士搭<br />\n所以呢啲車就啱啱好可以補充咗呢個空隙<br />\n又唔會影響司機搵食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最值得留意嘅係 呢架無人駕駛巴士幾乎係國產<br />\n車體硬件有7成都係 Made in taiwan<br />\n軟件直情100%台灣製造<br />\n<br />\ntaiwan number 1 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b263573d3a6c2572907fb4c623eb814317b4d58","tid":2093713,"uid":38737,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T04:55:40.000Z","msg":"果然係巴膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3885ddca82a825888ffd922f2dfb3ca68aa745ab","tid":2093713,"uid":2720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b263573d3a6c2572907fb4c623eb814317b4d58","tid":2093713,"uid":38737,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T04:55:40.000Z","msg":"果然係巴膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T04:57:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"020b4a5c4cdf84847